code: @Override public void act(final Client client, final Exchange exchange) throws NoSuchHeaderException {     final Long jobId = BeanstalkExchangeHelper.getJobID(exchange).     final boolean result = client.delete(jobId).     if (!result && LOG.isWarnEnabled()) {         LOG.warn(String.format("Failed to delete job %d", jobId)).     } else if (LOG.isDebugEnabled()) {         LOG.debug(String.format("Job %d deleted. Result is %b", jobId, result)).     }     answerWith(exchange, Headers.RESULT, result). }
